---
title: Blackened White Bass with Crispy Potatoes and Blistered Summer Vegetables
description: For a lighter preparation of the Southern take on battered fish, we’re blackening a local Lake Erie fish with a potent mix of spices. A side of crispy roasted potatoes and caramelized vegetables complements the dish!
